data.description: Beautifully updated home in desirable Golden Meadows Subdivision. This 3-bedroom 2-bathroom home is move in ready. Accent wall in dining room, newer fixtures throughout, neutral soft paint colors, newer flooring. Screened in front entry area, larger fully fenced back yard with storage shed and covered parking perfect for a boat or other items. Close to Barksdale Air Force Base, shopping, dining, and more. This one is a must see.
